NEW ORLEANS - Saints head coach Sean Payton said he understands the rumors about other teams wanting him after a 10-year run in New Orleans that has currently hit a rough patch. However, Payton said he sees himself here for a while. 
Payton, who has two years left on his deal with the team, said he recently bought a new home down here and sees himself here for "many years."
